CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.austin_waste.waste_and_diversion`
(
  load_id INT64,
  report_date DATE,
  load_type STRING,
  load_time TIMESTAMP,
  load_weight FLOAT64,
  dropoff_site STRING,
  route_type STRING,
  route_number STRING
)
OPTIONS(
  description="Austin waste and diversion"
);
